data.title: Crick (Short 2019)
data.meta_description: Crick: Directed by Justin R. Durban. With Nikki M. Weiland, Brett St. Germain, Jordan O'Neal, Tabitha Thompson. A simple a story of revenge. But it doesn't have to be. There's an alternate universe of possibilities and we never know what the world will bring when someone in a mask comes knocking on your door. You - have the choice to answer.
